issue.title: Access raw body and json body
issue.body:
Hi,

how can I get the raw body and also the json body from a request?
Currently I use 
```
Picker.middleware( bodyParser.json() );
```
And this works fine, but for security checks I would also need the raw body. How could I get both of them?

Best,
Gerwin

comment.body: @gerwinbrunner Re: raw body. Have you tried just passing a function to `Picker.middleware` that listens for `'data'`?

release.name: Logged errors muted too
release.body:
`stderr` is also muted now. `.resume('preserve')` works as expected. Retrieved data from `.resume` is now an object with arrays on `.stderr` and `.stdout`. See README for details.

This might be considered a breaking change but we're still on 0.x so I guess that's ok.
